N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5612.3 - Proof of compliance

State Regulations

The registrant shall maintain any information and
materials necessary to demonstrate such registrant's compliance with this Part. Registrants may be required by the commission to maintain additional records
and information where there is cause to believe the registrant is not complying
with this Part. Notes
